@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_caiwra(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.22 - v2 + 0.25)) + ((v1 + 0.99 - v2 + 0.40) / (tmp + 0.30 / v1 + 0.87)))
    v1 = wp.exp((0.31 + (v1 + 0.67 * v2 + 0.50)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.34 - v1 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
